{"tid":483811,"cid":23,"subCid":0,"title":"Sony A7RIII R3 用家揮手區","createTime":"2017-11-29T13:09:23.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-05T17:19:34.000Z","uid":129686,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"c53648d07affb398513f1263d29007b9d2e31435","tid":483811,"uid":129686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T13:09:23.000Z","msg":"今日取機，齋機"},{"pid":"f84c6f99fb5fce59cc6a362bcf278050b8312216","tid":483811,"uid":89757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T13:11:30.000Z","msg":"有冇舊機放<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc7894ea03ab0c349fe66cafa1c089218643a7a4","tid":483811,"uid":28001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T13:28:13.000Z","msg":"尋晚拎咗今日玩足一日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02c45238aa69e820e843d5941de13f1c3b460877","tid":483811,"uid":74102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T13:48:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>尋晚拎咗今日玩足一日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打對部機有咩評價<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65caa9a0871b94cf35c961baa64316c3e228a677","tid":483811,"uid":28001,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T14:11:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>尋晚拎咗今日玩足一日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打對部機有咩評價<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n以前A7R2用家嘅感覺<br />\n<br />\n1) 對焦明顯快咗，唔多覺有hunting現象，成部機操作都快咗好多<br />\n2) Pixel Shift 實用性低，除非你真係好執著zoom 100%聞detail<br />\n3) 快門完全唔同聲，爽快好多同震動減輕咗。shutter lag感覺輕微好多<br />\n4) 寫buffer比想象中快，清buffer途中可以入menu可以preview相<br />\n5) 部機重咗, 就算無裝L plate都好揸咗<br />\n6) 高iso 表現好咗，無一級但比R2 好咗大概1/3 or 1/4級左右。 low iso 畫質睇唔到分別.<br />\n7) Auto WB好咗少少，無R2咁冷色<br />\n8) 可能我盲 LCD同EVF升級分別個人覺得唔明顯,但LCD色溫同gamma 標準咗d.<br />\n9) 啲轉盤好轉非常多！ 緊得嚟唔會難轉但唔會好似R2咁鬆容易high到。<br />\n    PASM轉盤好轉好多，R2果個緊到差啲要用士巴拿轉..<br />\n10) touchscreen反映比想像中慢，但可接受。 joystick 一個字正<br />\n11) 有My Menus Setting <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n12) evf/lcd auto 個靈敏度正常好多，同埋你如果反咗個LCD出來<br />\n      evf/lcd auto switch會自動disable, 腰平影唔會再無啦啦自己轉evf<br />\n13) 粒電有料到，今日玩左一日無換過電<br />\n14) Uncompressed RAW preview快咗幾十倍，以前我用R2 set咗影RAW+JPG(11mp), 因為要zoom in 個RAW file要7,8秒最少..R3幾乎秒zoom<br />\n而家改番影RAW only, 慳番啲位<br />\n<br />\n整體評價： <br />\n升級感非常大，用過R3之後覺得R2好似史前相機. 一部除咗畫質之外咩都冇嘅相機。如果有閒錢強烈建議升級，R3將我以前用R2用得唔爽嘅問題解決晒.<br />\n唯一希望之後有辦法裝app， 唔係要裝Sony d 垃圾APP<br />\n我係要裝Openmemories Tweak呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n或者之後有辦法破解29.59秒錄影限制都ok! 希望啲大佬快啲諗諗計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d64e9c7c36c15b614c0ff50d99f7338e1c620bc","tid":483811,"uid":28001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T14:13:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>尋晚拎咗今日玩足一日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打對部機有咩評價<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n以前A7R2用家嘅感覺<br />\n<br />\n1) 對焦明顯快咗，唔多覺有hunting現象，成部機操作都快咗好多<br />\n2) Pixel Shift 實用性低，除非你真係好執著zoom 100%聞detail<br />\n3) 快門完全唔同聲，爽快好多同震動減輕咗。shutter lag感覺輕微好多<br />\n4) 寫buffer比想象中快，清buffer途中可以入menu可以preview相<br />\n5) 部機重咗, 就算無裝L plate都好揸咗<br />\n6) 高iso 表現好咗，無一級但比R2 好咗大概1/3 or 1/4級左右。 low iso 畫質睇唔到分別.<br />\n7) Auto WB好咗少少，無R2咁冷色<br />\n8) 可能我盲 LCD同EVF升級分別個人覺得唔明顯,但LCD色溫同gamma 標準咗d.<br />\n9) 啲轉盤好轉非常多！ 緊得嚟唔會難轉但唔會好似R2咁鬆容易high到。<br />\n    PASM轉盤好轉好多，R2果個緊到差啲要用士巴拿轉..<br />\n10) touchscreen反映比想像中慢，但可接受。 joystick 一個字正<br />\n11) 有My Menus Setting <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n12) evf/lcd auto 個靈敏度正常好多，同埋你如果反咗個LCD出來<br />\n      evf/lcd auto switch會自動disable, 腰平影唔會再無啦啦自己轉evf<br />\n13) 粒電有料到，今日玩左一日無換過電<br />\n14) Uncompressed RAW preview快咗幾十倍，以前我用R2 set咗影RAW+JPG(11mp), 因為要zoom in 個RAW file要7,8秒最少..R3幾乎秒zoom<br />\n而家改番影RAW only, 慳番啲位<br />\n<br />\n整體評價： <br />\n升級感非常大，用過R3之後覺得R2好似史前相機. 一部除咗畫質之外咩都冇嘅相機。如果有閒錢強烈建議升級，R3將我以前用R2用得唔爽嘅問題解決晒.<br />\n唯一希望之後有辦法裝app， 唔係要裝Sony d 垃圾APP<br />\n我係要裝Openmemories Tweak呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n或者之後有辦法破解29<span style=\"color: red;\">分</span>59秒錄影限制都ok! 希望啲大佬快啲諗諗計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"ada2363386a28156949b24313110c9697c2c0972","tid":483811,"uid":15592,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T14:16:42.000Z","msg":"剛剛今晚拎機，而家差電中<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n由nikon轉到sony，又第一次用sony機，睇黎要花d時間刨下本manual <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nbtw，其實compressed同uncompressed raw個quality差得遠唔遠？"},{"pid":"cdcb16f6eff4610a19104e8a4a987f57bc40b052","tid":483811,"uid":28001,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T14:26:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>剛剛今晚拎機，而家差電中<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n由nikon轉到sony，又第一次用sony機，睇黎要花d時間刨下本manual <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nbtw，其實compressed同uncompressed raw個quality差得遠唔遠？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nSony機肯定冇Nikon咁好用架嘞，我諗巴打要時間適應下。<br />\n2者差好少，絕大部分情況直頭冇分別<br />\n不過而家啲card咁大容量。我都係影uncompressed算.."},{"pid":"7be701261e90136e87d42fdb569c4308dc45edb0","tid":483811,"uid":15592,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T14:42:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>剛剛今晚拎機，而家差電中<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n由nikon轉到sony，又第一次用sony機，睇黎要花d時間刨下本manual <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nbtw，其實compressed同uncompressed raw個quality差得遠唔遠？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nSony機肯定冇Nikon咁好用架嘞，我諗巴打要時間適應下。<br />\n2者差好少，絕大部分情況直頭冇分別<br />\n不過而家啲card咁大容量。我都係影uncompressed算..</blockquote><br />\n我連埋支24-105買，玩左陣覺得對焦好爽快，尤其d暗位對焦快過我部d750 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n暫時最唔慣係感覺個快門輕過單反好多，㩒制影相果下有d唔實在 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f304be2c434a460081b88ae4839645381f0fa36","tid":483811,"uid":28001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T14:54:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>剛剛今晚拎機，而家差電中<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n由nikon轉到sony，又第一次用sony機，睇黎要花d時間刨下本manual <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nbtw，其實compressed同uncompressed raw個quality差得遠唔遠？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nSony機肯定冇Nikon咁好用架嘞，我諗巴打要時間適應下。<br />\n2者差好少，絕大部分情況直頭冇分別<br />\n不過而家啲card咁大容量。我都係影uncompressed算..</blockquote><br />\n我連埋支<span style=\"color: red;\">24-105</span>買，玩左陣覺得對焦好爽快，尤其d暗位對焦快過我部d750 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n暫時最唔慣係感覺個快門輕過單反好多，㩒制影相果下有d唔實在 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  me無錢買<br />\n咁差咁多年，科技肯定好好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eac