><br />\n<br />\n咁如果行雙卡同時save raw+jpg 咪即係以前咁等到hihi?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係呀我試咗。如果揀simul slot 1 + 2<br />\nclear buffer 時間會變成UHS-I 速度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果你想維持高速clear buffer <br />\n只可以寫Slot 1 之後自己手動耐唔耐copy slot 1 to slot 2<br />\n<br />\n我暫時用緊slot 1(Sandisk extreme pro 128) 寫相， slot 2 (Lexar 1000x 256GB) 寫片. <br />\n之後再研究下有咩好啲嘅方法做backup方案</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n師兄等你報告<br />\n我得跟機張64G快卡，未買128G sandisk 95<br />\nBTW, sandisk 95, 我見有張有v30, 但有張無， 暫時查唔到係咪一樣。"},{"pid":"b6422ff669c3916ba103b71b91a00f8ffb1d109f","tid":483811,"uid":48631,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T08:35:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>其實舊個粒電係咪冇辦法兼容到,屌佢老母買撚左差唔多成打電<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實DIY有辦法，但好on9 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n本身換機其中一個點就係新電耐頂好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我明呀,但係成手電,二手監平監賤賣左佢又好柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"167e8a8559344e3fbf4be5b1e7b6353e8ce519ab","tid":483811,"uid":10232,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T08:50:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n咩價錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nX2...有興趣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nSd card 800<br />\n電 500<br />\n有意請留tg thx</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n勁喎巴打，賣得仲貴過Sony Store <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我睇<a href=\"http://price.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fprice.com&d=1qt1NV1hyxuiDEhoTKi0XcmB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=2627ede6\" target=\"_blank\">http://price.com</a> 個價<br />\nSd card 最平係83